---
// Print-blocking stylesheet for the read-only guest view.
// Include ONLY when the current user is a guest (role 'gast') so that
// Ctrl+P / "Save as PDF" cannot be used to extract the rendered content.
// It hides every top-level body element on print and shows a short notice
// instead (a pseudo-element survives the display:none on real elements).
---
<style is:global>
  @media print {
    body > * { display: none !important; }
    body::after {
      content: "Drucken ist in der Gast-Ansicht deaktiviert. Bitte mit einem BBW-Konto anmelden.";
      display: block !important;
      padding: 40px;
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #334155;
    }
  }
</style>
